text.section:
This section does not apply to:
The room of a registered guest in a hotel, motel, or hospice;
The property of a volunteer fire company; or
Any of the following entities in continuous existence in Worcester County since October 1, 1989:
A catering establishment;
A community or civic association;
A swim club;
A bona fide social, civic, nonprofit, charitable, fraternal, patriotic, educational, or public service organization; or
A bona fide religious institution.
